562744470333292540,Tue Feb 03 22:48:31 +0000 2015,@CineKink thank you so much for engaging. It's important we do.
562744089016557600,Tue Feb 03 22:47:00 +0000 2015,@CineKink exactly! Everyone's desires are different. You wouldn't think so based on content. I'm bored w/one-note mainstream sexualization!
562743541508878340,Tue Feb 03 22:44:50 +0000 2015,@CineKink yes, agreed. I think ultimately, we all want the same thing. Choice &  equality &  GENUINE empowerment for women in any industry.
562714728196481000,Tue Feb 03 20:50:20 +0000 2015,@kittystryker i think seeing it is the only way to know! Thanks for being open and discussing with me :)
562714136581533700,Tue Feb 03 20:47:59 +0000 2015,@kittystryker of course.But wouldn't someone from the inside have a bias too? The filmmakers are journalists. Their goal was to be balanced.
562711834374176800,Tue Feb 03 20:38:50 +0000 2015,@kittystryker my intention is not to shame but to share stories. yes, every industry deserves equal respect, protection & worker's rights.
562711296484077600,Tue Feb 03 20:36:42 +0000 2015,@kittystryker I totally agree. We are on the same side of the argument.
562711174782156800,Tue Feb 03 20:36:13 +0000 2015,@kittystryker that's fantastic!! And there needs to be more!! I'm only trying to shed some light on those who are not as dedicated as you.
562709758365696000,Tue Feb 03 20:30:35 +0000 2015,@CineKink a lot of loopholes in the wild west of porn industry that seem to be exploited.  Really want to open up a dialogue about this.
562709378126843900,Tue Feb 03 20:29:05 +0000 2015,@CineKink many stories to be told from porn world. I'm pro-sex, anti-exploitation. Good experiences don't negate bad ones. & vice versa.
562708991013560300,Tue Feb 03 20:27:32 +0000 2015,@kittystryker of course porn movies, Hollywood movies, anything that depends on performances, is going to be performative. It's axiomatic.
562708476858994700,Tue Feb 03 20:25:30 +0000 2015,@kittystryker my gripe is that SOCIO-CULTURALLY, we seem more interested in performative sexuality" than actual sexual pleasure for women.
